"title": "4017: life, animal and plant",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4017: life, animal and plant",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All living creatures and plants were made by God and are sustained by him.</p>\n<h2>Animal life</h2>\n<h3>Animals were created by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:19\">GEN 2:19</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:24\">PSA 104:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:20-Gen1:25\">GEN 1:20–1:25</a></p>\n<h3>Animals are cared for by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:15-Ps145:16\">PSA 145:15–145:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:26\">MAT 6:26</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:24\">LUK 12:24</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:7\">DEU 22:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:10-Ps104:12\">PSA 104:10–104:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:14\">PSA 104:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:17-Ps104:18\">PSA 104:17–104:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:21\">PSA 104:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:27\">PSA 104:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps136:25\">PSA 136:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:9\">PSA 147:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah4:11\">JON 4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:29\">MAT 10:29</a></p>\n<h3>Animal life is controlled by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:22\">DAN 6:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:28\">NUM 22:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:17\">JON 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:33\">HEB 11:33</a></p>\n<h3>Animal life has been placed under human care</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26\">GEN 1:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">GEN 1:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:19\">GEN 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:2\">GEN 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:6-Ps8:8\">PSA 8:6–8:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:38\">DAN 2:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:8\">HEB 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:7\">JAS 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Animals serve human needs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:21\">GEN 3:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:1-Matt21:3\">MAT 21:1–21:3</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:1-Mark11:3\">MRK 11:1–11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:29-Luke19:31\">LUK 19:29–19:31</a></p>\n<h3>Animal life saved by Noah from the flood</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:19-Gen6:22\">GEN 6:19–6:22</a></p>\n<h3>Animals subsequently given to humanity for food</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:3-Gen9:4\">GEN 9:3–9:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:20-Deut12:25\">DEU 12:20–12:25</a></p>\n<h3>Clean and unclean animals</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:2-Gen7:3\">GEN 7:2–7:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev11:47\">LEV 11:47</a></p>\n<h3>Animals used in sacrifice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:4\">GEN 4:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen8:20\">GEN 8:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev17:11\">LEV 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:22\">HEB 9:22</a></p>\n<h3>Animal life glorifies God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps148:7\">PSA 148:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps150:6\">PSA 150:6</a></p>\n<h2>Plant life</h2>\n<h3>Plants were created by God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:11-Gen1:12\">GEN 1:11–1:12</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Plant life is often short-lived</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:30\">MAT 6:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:28\">LUK 12:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:5-Ps90:6\">PSA 90:5–90:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:15-Ps103:16\">PSA 103:15–103:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:27\">ISA 37:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:12\">ISA 51:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:24\">1PE 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:8\">ISA 40:6–40:8</a></p>\n<h3>Plants are provided for food</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:29-Gen1:30\">GEN 1:29–1:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:16-Gen2:17\">GEN 2:16–2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:2\">GEN 3:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:3\">GEN 9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:5\">1KI 18:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job28:5\">JOB 28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:14\">PSA 104:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:8-Ps147:9\">PSA 147:8–147:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:32\">DAN 4:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:22\">JOL 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>Plant life glorifies God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps96:12-Ps96:13\">PSA 96:12–96:13</a></p>",
